dct_title_s: Plan de Paris : à l'échelle de 1/10,000
dct_description_sm: "T.3929." "Reproduction interdite." Map shows Paris neighborhoods, streets, and sites of interest. Differs from edition also issued in 1956 in that its scale is 1:15,000 rather than 1:10,000.
dct_creator_sm: Seine (France). Préfecture. Services techniques de topographie et d'urbanisme
dct_publisher_sm: Paris : Services techniques de topographie et d'urbanisme, 1956.
